title: Showtunes (Tommy Keene album)
text:
Showtunes is a live album by <a href="Tommy%20Keene">Tommy Keene</a>. It came out in 2000 on the <a href="Parasol%20Records">Parasol Records</a> label. Along with in-concert versions of original compositions, the album includes a <a href="cover%20version">cover version</a> of <a href="Mission%20of%20Burma">Mission of Burma</a>'s "Einstein's Day".
Track listing.
All songs by Tommy Keene, except where noted.
